{"tid":663364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[2018-04-17]機電署新增13個職位加強升降機安全　額外開支達730萬","createTime":"2018-05-13T08:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T02:47:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa85e340b473bae9138ebff48c0ef9311ab33036","tid":663364,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"本港接連發生升降機事故，包括朗豪坊的扶手電梯意外以及荃灣海灣花園的升降機突然急升等事故，引起社會關注。立法會財務委員會將於本周四（19日）召開特別會議，審核2018/19財政年度的開支預算，機電工程署透過書面回覆，透露於2018/19年度，署方擬<span style=\"color: red;\">增聘13名人手加入安全專責隊伍，預算額外開支為730萬。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/179203/%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E13%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E9%A1%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E9%81%94730%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F179203%2F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E13%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E9%25A1%258D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E9%2581%2594730%25E8%2590%25AC&d=%2FzRVnhu9iKgVEFvl1lOf0DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4165dd31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/179203/%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E13%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E9%A1%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E9%81%94730%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"899e9b618582eb9b1cff26374f3d2134faa21452","tid":663364,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\"